snippet.title: Best VGM 1420 - Castlevania III - Rising
snippet.description:
See also:
Best VGM 696 - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=VpyUtWCMrb4
Best VGM 2273 - https://youtu.be/bt0FCsafudU

A collection of my favorite videogame music. Note that most of them are from games I played so I might miss some great ones from games I never played.

NES
Castlevania III : Dracula's Curse (1990)
Rising
Hidenori Maezawa, Jun Funahashi & Yukie Morimoto
